        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "那么……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 35,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "里芙无限之视",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这一切该结束了。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 36,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "沙发上，里芙缓缓睁开双眼。下一秒，她扑进我的怀里，双手紧紧地环绕在我的背后。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 37,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "如同一个刚被救上岸的溺水者，急促而杂乱的气息喷在我的颈侧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": 38,
        "Flag": "",
        "Pos": 0,
        "Speaker": "",
        "RealSpeaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我以更大的力度回抱着她，直到她渐渐平复。",
        "disable": 0
